cw_1201592

Class Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • cw_1201592.Tag

  • public class Tag
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores data for a tag provided by users. Instances of this class store:
    • the name of the tag, as a string.
    There are operations to set and get the field value, to get the hash code the Tag object and to compare whether two Tag objects are equal or not in terms of name.
    Author:
    Boqing Liu
